ce%20means%20that%20the%20industrywide%20rate%20of%20customer%20defections%2C%20which%20has%20risen%20over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20is%20less%20pronounced%20than%20it%20appears.%20The%20average%20rate%20of%20U.S.%20customer%20cancellations%20among%20premium%20streaming%20video%20services%20reached%205.2%25%20in%20August%2C%20but%20after%20factoring%20in%20re-subscribers%2C%20the%20rate%20of%20defections%20was%20lower%20at%203.5%25.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20last%20month%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fftc-cancel-subscriptions-rule-click-to-cancel-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFederal%20Trade%20Commission%20finalized%20a%20%26quot%3Bclick%20to%20cancel%26quot%3B%20rule%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20is%20supposed%20to%20make%20it%20easier%20for%20customers%20to%20cancel%20online%20subscriptions.%20(The%20rule%20essentially%20says%20if%20you%20signed%20up%20online%2C%20you%20can't%20be%20required%20to%20cancel%20by%20phone%20or%20mail%20%E2%80%94%20you%20have%20to%20be%20able%20to%20cancel%20online%2C%20too.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20experience%2C%20streamers%20generally%20are%20already%20compliant%20with%20the%20FTC's%20rule.%20Because%20of%20that%2C%20I%20doubt%20it's%20going%20to%20have%20much%20effect%20on%20whether%20someone%20cancels.%20Instead%2C%20streamers%20might%20offer%20discounts%2C%20promotions%2C%20or%20bundling%20with%20other%20services%20to%20try%20to%20keep%20you%20for%20the%20long%20term%20and%20reduce%20what%20they%20call%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstreaming-bundle-max-disney-hulu-warner-bros-discovery-wbd-netflix-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echurn%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20me%2C%20I'm%20back%20as%20a%20happy%20Hulu%20subscriber%20after%20I%20was%20lured%20by%20comedian%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F11%2F05%2Fstyle%2Fbrian-jordan-alvarez-english-teacher-tiktok.