e%20NYT%20Games%20and%20Cooking%20apps%20and%20is%20fighting%20for%20fair%20labor%20conditions.%20(Photo%20by%20Erik%20McGregor%2FLightRocket%20via%20Getty%20Images)%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67326f965ec9bfa3d63d5b89%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222063%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENew%20York%20Times%20Tech%20Guild%20members%20gathered%20outside%20the%20outlet's%20headquarters%20in%20Manhattan%20during%20the%20strike.%3Cp%3EErik%20McGregor%2FLightRocket%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ENew%20York%20Times%20tech%20workers%20are%20ending%20their%20strike%20after%20a%20weeklong%20stoppage.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20strike%20threatened%20to%20disrupt%20election%20coverage%20but%20had%20limited%20impact%20on%20the%20Times'%20operations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Tech%20Guild%2C%20formed%20in%202021%2C%20represents%20600-plus%20engineers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20York%20Times%20tech%20workers%20are%20ending%20their%20strike%20and%20returning%20to%20work%20Tuesday%20after%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-york-times-tech-strike-disrupt-site-election-coverage-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eweeklong%20work%20stoppage%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Tech%20Guild%20chose%20a%20crucial%20day%20to%20go%20on%20strike%2C%20the%20day%20before%20the%20November%205%20US%20presidential%20election%2C%20in%20a%20move%20that%20threatened%20to%20disrupt%20the%20paper's%20important%20election%20coverage.%20Its%20parent%2C%20the%20New%20Guild-CWA%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnewsguild.org%2Fnewsletter-election-day-strike-at-the-new-york-times%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecalled%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20the%20%26quot%3Blargest%20tech%20worker%20strike%20in%20US%20history.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Times'%20site%20and%20its%20famous%20election%20needle%20that%20shows%20how%20a%20race%20is%20tilting%20operated%20j