orld%2Fus%2Fwatch-sister-in-law-lara-trump-jokes-about-barron-trumps-height-i-am-511%2Famp_articleshow%2F115191793.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22COP29%3A%20What%20Is%20A%20Carbon%20Credit%3F%20What%20Is%20Article%206%3F%20Top%20Questions%20Answered%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECountries%20at%20the%20United%20Nations%20COP29%20climate%20summit%20in%20Azerbaijan%20will%20attempt%20to%20agree%20rules%20for%20a%20global%20system%20for%20trading%20carbon%20offset%20credits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20what%20you%20should%20know%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHAT%20ARE%20CARBON%20OFFSETS%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20governments%20and%20companies%20may%20struggle%20to%20reduce%20their%20planet-warming%20greenhouse%20gas%20emissions%20to%20meet%20their%20climate%20targets.%20Supporters%20of%20carbon%20offsets%20see%20them%20as%20a%20key%20means%20to%20help%20meet%20these%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20offsets%20allow%20one%20nation%20or%20company%20to%20offset%20some%20of%20their%20emissions%20by%20paying%20for%20actions%20to%20cut%20emissions%20elsewhere.%20These%20actions%20might%20include%20rural%20solar%20panel%20installations%20or%20converting%20a%20fleet%20of%20petrol%20buses%20to%20electric.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHAT%20IS%20ARTICLE%206%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArticle%206%20of%20the%20Paris%20Agreement%20helps%20countries%20work%20together%20to%20reduce%20their%20carbon%20emissions.%20It%20sets%20out%20two%20options%20for%20countries%20and%20companies%20to%20trade%20offsets%2C%20helping%20them%20meet%20the%20goals%20they%20set%20to%20reduce%20planetary-warming%20gases%20in%20their%20climate%20action%20plans%2C%20known%20as%20nationally%20determined%20contributions%20(NDCs).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20allows%20two%20countries%20to%20set%20their%20own%20terms%20for%20a%20bilateral%20carbon%20trading%20agreement%2C%20this%20is%20known%20as%20Article%206.2.%20The%20second%20aims%20to%20create%20a%20central%2C%20UN-managed%20system%20for%20countries%20and%20companies%20to%20begin%20offsetting%20their%20carbon%20emissions%20and%20trading%20those%20offsets%2C%20known%20as%20Article%206.4.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArticle%206%20is%20seen%20an%20important%20mechanism%20for%20delivering%20climate%20finance%20to%20developing%20countries%2C%20and%20a%20Paris%20Agreement%20carbon%20market%2C%20if%20launched%2C%20could%20continue%20operating%20even%20if%20the%20United%20States%20under%20Donald%20Trump%20withdraws%20support%20for%20the%20Paris%20Agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHAT'S%20BEEN%20DECIDED%20SO%20FAR%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20COP26%20climate%20summit%20in%20Glasgow%2C%20negotiators%20reached%20a%20breakthrough%20agreement%20that%20established%20a%20broad%20rulebook%20to%20regulate%20trading%20of%20carbon%20credits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20after%20two%20weeks%20of%20talks%20at%20COP28%20in%20Dubai%2C%20countries%20failed%20to%20seal%20a%20deal%20on%20necessary%20details%20to%20operationalise%20a%20central%20carbon%20trading%20system%20or%20to%20clarify%20rules%20for%20nations%20wanting%20to%20make%20bilateral%20arrangements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20countries%20like%20Japan%20and%20Indonesia%20have%20decided%20to%20press%20ahead%20with%20bilateral%20agreements%20without%20those%20clarifications%20and%20are%20already%20preparing%20to%20trade%20carbon%20credits%2C%20known%20as%20%26quot%3Binternationally%20transferable%20mitigation%20outcomes%26quot%3B%20(ITMOs).%20The%20UN%20says%2091%20agreements%20had%20been%20made%20between%2056%20countries%20as%20of%20October%20this%20year.%20Thailand%20and%20Switzerland%20completed%20the%20first%20sale%20in%20January%2C%20and%20the%20market%20for%20bilateral%20trade%20agreements%20is%20still%20quite%20small.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20buyers%20are%20worried%20there%20are%20not%20adequate%20rules%20to%20stop%20countries%20changing%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20agreements%2C%20or%20revoking%20them%2C%20and%20that%20there%20is%20not%20a%20robust%20system%20to%20ensure%20that%20credits%20bought%20and%20sold%20are%20not%20being%20counted%20by%20both%20the%20buying%20and%20selling%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHAT%20WILL%20BE%20DECIDED%20AT%20COP29%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20are%20keen%20to%20secure%20an%20early%20%26quot%3Bwin%26quot%3B%20on%20Article%206%20at%20this%20year's%20climate%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarket%20watchers%20are%20hopeful%20an%20agreement%20can%20be%20reached%20to%20set%20guardrails%20for%20the%20bilateral%20agreements%20and%20to%20operationalise%20the%20UN-backed%20centralised%20marketplace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGuardrails%20include%20checks%20and%20balances%20to%20provide%20assurance%20countries%20are%20buying%20and%20selling%20actual%20emissions%20reductions.%20Some%20countries%20for%20example%20want%20methods%20nations%20use%20to%20generate%20credits%20to%20be%20checked%20internationally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECountries%20will%20also%20negotiate%20whether%20the%20UN's%20central%20registry%20can%20itself%20house%20credits%20that%20can%20be%20transacted%20and%20retired%20or%20whether%20it%20should%20operate%20just%20for%20accounting%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20expert%20group%20elected%20under%20United%20Nations%20rules%20has%20already%20hammered%20out%20a%20framework%20for%20the%20multilateral%20trading%20system%20to%20ensure%20credits%20meet%20basic%20quality%20standards.%20But%20countries%20at%20COP29%20can%20decide%20to%20either%20sign%20off%20on%20this%20standard%2C%20open%20up%20further%20discussions%2C%20or%20reject%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20COP29%2C%20the%20technical%20expert%20group%20will%20meet%20again%20to%20agree%20which%20methodologies%20for%20generating%20carbon%20credits%20through%20cookstoves%20projects%20or%20reforestation%20for%20example%20can%20issue%20credits%20into%20the%20new%20Paris%20Aligned%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20key%20points%20are%20resolved%20this%20year%2C%20the%20system%20could%20launch%20as%20soon%20as%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHAT%20DOES%20THIS%20MEAN%20FOR%20THE%20VOLUNTARY%20CARBON%20MARKET%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20companies%20that%20are%20under%20no%20legal%20obligation%20to%20cut%20their%20emissions%20have%20set%20voluntary%20targets%2C%20which%20they%20can%20meet%20partially%20through%20buying%20credits%20on%20a%20voluntary%20carbon%20market.%20In%202022%2C%20the%20voluntary%20market%20was%20valued%20at%20about%20%242%20billion%20worldwide.%20But%20the%20market%20value%20plummeted%20to%20%24723%20million%20last%20year%20after%20being%20shaken%20by%20repeated%20scandals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELinking%20up%20carbon%20projects%20currently%20in%20the%20voluntary%20market%20with%20the%20Paris%20Agreement%20system%20could%20boost%20confidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevelopers%20of%20projects%20like%20mangrove%20restoration%20to%20regenerative%20agriculture%20can%20apply%20to%20have%20their%20credits%20sold%20under%20the%20UN%20system%2C%20meaning%20that%20if%20approved%2C%20they%20could%20sell%20in%20either%20that%20system%20or%20on%20the%20voluntary%20market.%20Experts%20expect%20UN-approved%20credits%20to%20carry%20a%20higher%20price%20tag.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731350340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fjjlggl0c_cop29-climate-summit-reuters_625x300_12_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcop29-climate-summit-what-is-a-carbon-credit-what-is-article-6-top-questions-answered-6996927%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Countries%20at%20the%20United%20Nations%20COP29%20climate%20summit%20in%20Azerbaijan%20will%20attempt%20to%20agree%20rules%20for%20a%20global%20system%20for%20trading%20carbon%20offset%20credits.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amazon%20developing%20driver%20eyeglasses%20to%20shave%20seconds%20off%20deliveries%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731349541000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Famazon-developing-driver-eyeglasses-to-shave-seconds-off-deliveries-124111101817_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20successful%2C%20the%20glasses%20would%20provide%20drivers%20with%20turn-by-turn%20navigation%20on%20a%20small%20embedded%20screen%2C%20along%20their%20routes%20and%20at%20each%20stop%2C%20according%20to%20the%20people%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Famazon-developing-driver-eyeglasses-to-shave-seconds-off-deliveries-124111101817_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20Has%20Gotten%20What%20In%20Trump's%202nd%20Term%2C%20And%20Who's%20In%20The%20Running%20For%20One%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDonald%20Trump%20has%20begun%20the%20process%20of%20choosing%20a%20cabinet%20and%20selecting%20other%20high-ranking%20administration%20officials%20following%20his%20presidential%20election%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%20early%20picks%20and%20top%20contenders%20for%20some%20of%20the%20key%20posts%20overseeing%20defence%2C%20intelligence%2C%20diplomacy%2C%20trade%2C%20immigration%20and%20economic%20policymaking.%20Some%20are%20in%20contention%20for%20a%20range%20of%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESUSIE%20WILES%2C%20chief%20of%20staff%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20on%20Thursday%20announced%20that%20Wiles%2C%20one%20of%20his%20two%20campaign%20managers%2C%20will%20be%20his%20White%20House%20chief%20of%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20specifics%20of%20her%20political%20views%20are%20somewhat%20unclear%2C%20Wiles%2C%2067%2C%20is%20credited%20with%20running%20a%20successful%20and%20efficient%20campaign.%20Supporters%20hope%20she%20will%20instil%20a%20sense%20of%20order%20and%20discipline%20that%20was%20often%20lacking%20during%20Trump's%20first%20four-year%20term%20when%20he%20cycled%20through%20a%20number%20of%20chiefs%20of%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETOM%20HOMAN%2C%20'border%20czar'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20announced%20on%20Sunday%20night%20that%20Homan%2C%20the%20former%20acting%20director%20of%20Immigration%20and%20Customs%20Enforcement%20from%20his%20first%20administration%2C%20will%20be%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20country's%20borders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20made%20cracking%20down%20on%20people%20in%20the%20country%20illegally%20a%20central%20element%20of%20his%20campaign%2C%20promising%20mass%20deportations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHoman%20said%20on%20Monday%20he%20would%20prioritize%20deporting%20immigrants%20in%20the%20U.S.%20illegally%20who%20posed%20safety%20and%20security%20threats%20as%20well%20as%20those%20working%20at%20job%20sites.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%2C%20in%20a%20post%20on%20his%20Truth%20Social%20platform%2C%20said%20Homan%20will%20be%20%26quot%3Bin%20charge%20of%20our%20nation's%20borders%20(%26quot%3BThe%20Border%20Czar%26quot%3B)%2C%20including%2C%20but%20not%20limited%20to%2C%20the%20Southern%20Border%2C%20the%20Northern%20Border%2C%20all%20Maritime%2C%20and%20Aviation%20Security%2C%26quot%3B%20including%20the%20deportation%20of%20immigrants%20in%20the%20U.S.%20illegally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EELISE%20STEFANIK%2C%20U.N.%20ambassador%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20announced%20on%20Monday%20that%20Stefanik%2C%20a%20Republican%20congresswoman%20and%20staunch%20Trump%20supporter%2C%20would%20be%20his%20ambassador%20to%20the%20United%20Nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStefanik%2C%2040%2C%20a%20U.S.%20representative%20from%20New%20York%20state%20and%20House%20Republican%20conference%20chair%2C%20took%20a%20leadership%20position%20in%20the%20House%20of%20Representatives%20in%202021%20when%20she%20was%20elected%20to%20replace%20then-Representative%20Liz%20Cheney%2C%20who%20was%20ousted%20for%20criticizing%20Trump's%20false%20claims%20of%20election%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20honored%20to%20nominate%20Chairwoman%20Elise%20Stefanik%20to%20serve%20in%20my%20Cabinet%20as%20U.S.%20Ambassador%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BElise%20is%20an%20incredibly%20strong%2C%20tough%2C%20and%20smart%20America%20First%20fighter.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStefanik%20will%20arrive%20at%20the%20U.N.%20after%20bold%20promises%20by%20Trump%20to%20end%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%20and%20Israel's%20war%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESCOTT%20BESSENT%2C%20potential%20treasury%20secretary%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBessent%2C%20a%20key%20economic%20adviser%20to%20Trump%2C%20is%20widely%20seen%20as%20a%20top%20candidate%20for%20treasury%20secretary.%20A%20longtime%20hedge%20fund%20investor%20who%20taught%20at%20Yale%20University%20for%20several%20years%2C%20Bessent%20has%20a%20warm%20relationship%20with%20the%20president-elect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Bessent%20has%20long%20favored%20the%20laissez-faire%20policies%20that%20were%20popular%20in%20the%20pre-Trump%20Republican%20Party%2C%20he%20has%20also%20spoken%20highly%20of%20Trump's%20use%20of%20tariffs%20as%20a%20negotiating%20tool.%20He%20has%20praised%20the%20president-elect's%20economic%20philosophy%2C%20which%20rests%20on%20a%20skepticism%20of%20both%20regulations%20and%20international%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJOHN%20PAULSON%2C%20potential%20treasury%20secretary%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPaulson%2C%20a%20billionaire%20hedge%20fund%20manager%20and%20major%20Trump%20donor%2C%20is%20another%20top%20contender%20for%20treasury%20secretary.%20The%20longtime%20financier%20has%20told%20associates%20he%20would%20be%20interested%20in%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20longtime%20proponent%20of%20tax%20cuts%20and%20deregulation%2C%20Paulson's%20profile%20is%20broadly%20similar%20to%20that%20of%20other%20potential%20members%20of%20Trump's%20economic%20team.%20He%20has%20publicly%20supported%20targeted%20tariffs%20as%20a%20tool%20to%20ensure%20U.S.%20national%20security%20and%20combat%20unfair%20trade%20practices%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20high-profile%20fundraiser%20hosted%20by%20Paulson%20in%20April%20raked%20in%20over%20%2450%20million%20for%20the%20former%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELARRY%20KUDLOW%2C%20potential%20treasury%20secretary%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFox%20Business%20Network%20personality%20Larry%20Kudlow%2C%20who%20served%20as%20director%20of%20the%20National%20Economic%20Council%20for%20much%20of%20Trump's%20first%20term%2C%20has%20an%20outside%20shot%20at%20becoming%20his%20treasury%20secretary%20and%20would%20likely%20have%20an%20opportunity%20to%20take%20a%20separate%20economics-focused%20position%20if%20he%20is%20interested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20is%20privately%20skeptical%20of%20broad%20tariffs%2C%20there%20is%20publicly%20little%20daylight%20between%20the%20policies%20Kudlow%20advocates%20and%20those%20of%20the%20president-elect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EROBERT%20LIGHTHIZER%2C%20potential%20treasury%20secretary%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20loyalist%20who%20served%20as%20Trump's%20U.S.%20trade%20representative%20for%20essentially%20the%20then-president's%20entire%20term%2C%20Lighthizer%20will%20almost%20certainly%20be%20invited%20back.%20Though%20Bessent%20and%20Paulson%20likely%20have%20a%20better%20shot%20at%20becoming%20treasury%20secretary%2C%20Lighthizer%20has%20an%20outside%20chance%2C%20and%20he%20might%20be%20able%20to%20reprise%20his%20old%20role%20if%20he's%20interested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20Trump%2C%20Lighthizer%20is%20a%20trade%20skeptic%20and%20a%20firm%20believer%20in%20tariffs.%20He%20was%20one%20of%20the%20leading%20figures%20in%20Trump's%20trade%20war%20with%20China%20and%20the%20renegotiation%20of%20the%20North%20American%20Free%20Trade%20Agreement%2C%20or%20NAFTA%2C%20with%20Mexico%20and%20Canada%20during%20Trump's%20first%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHOWARD%20LUTNICK%2C%20potential%20treasury%20secretary%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20co-chair%20of%20Trump's%20transition%20effort%20and%20the%20longtime%20chief%20executive%20of%20financial%20services%20firm%20Cantor%20Fitzgerald%2C%20Lutnick%20is%20in%20the%20running%20for%20treasury%20secretary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bombastic%20New%20Yorker%20like%20Trump%2C%20Lutnick%20has%20uniformly%20praised%20the%20president-elect's%20economic%20policies%2C%20including%20his%20use%20of%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20at%20times%20given%20elaborate%2C%20unvarnished%20opinions%20about%20what%20policies%20will%20be%20enacted%20in%20Trump's%20second%20term.%20Some%20Trump%20allies%20had%20privately%20complained%20that%20he%20too%20often%20presented%20himself%20as%20speaking%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELINDA%20McMAHON%2C%20potential%20commerce%20secretary%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfessional%20wrestling%20magnate%20and%20former%20Small%20Business%20Administration%20director%20Linda%20McMahon%20is%20seen%20as%20the%20frontrunner%20to%20lead%20Trump's%20Department%20of%20Commerce%2C%20three%20sources%20briefed%20on%20the%20plans%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMcMahon%20is%20a%20major%20donor%20and%20was%20an%20early%20supporter%20of%20the%20Republican%20president-elect%20when%20he%20first%20ran%20for%20the%20White%20House%20almost%20a%20decade%20ago.%20This%20time%2C%20Trump%20tapped%20her%20to%20co-lead%20a%20transition%20team%20formed%20to%20help%20vet%20personnel%20and%20draft%20policy%20ahead%20of%20the%20Nov.%205%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMcMahon%20is%20the%20co-founder%20and%20former%20CEO%20of%20the%20professional%20wrestling%20franchise%20WWE.%20She%20later%20served%20as%20director%20of%20the%20Small%20Business%20Administration%2C%20resigning%20in%202019%2C%20and%20went%20on%20to%20lead%20a%20pro-Trump%20political%20action%20committee%20that%20supported%20his%202020%20reelection%20bid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERICHARD%20GRENELL%2C%20potential%20secretary%20of%20state%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrenell%20is%20among%20Trump's%20closest%20foreign%20policy%20advisers.%20During%20the%20president-elect's%20first%20four-year%20term%2C%20he%20served%20as%20acting%20director%20of%20national%20intelligence%20and%20U.S.%20ambassador%20to%20Germany.%20When%20Trump%20met%20with%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskiy%20in%20September%2C%20Grenell%20sat%20in%20on%20the%20private%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrenell's%20private%20dealings%20with%20foreign%20leaders%20and%20often-caustic%20personality%20have%20made%20him%20the%20center%20of%20multiple%20controversies%2C%20though%20significant%20Republican%20gains%20in%20the%20Senate%20mean%20he%20could%20likely%20be%20confirmed.%20He%20is%20also%20considered%20a%20top%20contender%20for%20national%20security%20adviser%2C%20which%20does%20not%20require%20Senate%20confirmation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20policies%20he%20has%20advocated%20for%20is%20setting%20up%20an%20autonomous%20zone%20in%20eastern%20Ukraine%20to%20end%20the%20war%20there%2C%20a%20position%20Kyiv%20considers%20unacceptable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EROBERT%20O'BRIEN%2C%20potential%20secretary%20of%20state%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EO'Brien%2C%20Trump's%20fourth%20and%20final%20national%20security%20adviser%20during%20his%20first%20term%2C%20maintains%20a%20close%20relationship%20with%20Trump%2C%20and%20the%20two%20often%20speak%20on%20national%20security%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20likely%20in%20the%20running%20for%20secretary%20of%20state%20or%20other%20top%20foreign%20policy%20and%20national%20security%20posts.%20He%20has%20maintained%20close%20contacts%20with%20foreign%20leaders%20since%20Trump%20left%20office%2C%20having%20met%20with%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20in%20Israel%20in%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20views%20are%20somewhat%20more%20hawkish%20than%20some%20of%20Trump's%20advisers.%20He%20has%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20been%20more%20supportive%20of%20military%20aid%20for%20Ukraine%20than%20many%20of%20his%20Republican%20contemporaries%2C%20and%20he%20is%20a%20proponent%20of%20banning%20TikTok%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBILL%20HAGERTY%2C%20potential%20secretary%20of%20state%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20U.S.%20senator%20from%20Tennessee%20who%20worked%20on%20Trump's%202016%20transition%20effort%2C%20Hagerty%20is%20considered%20a%20top%20contender%20for%20secretary%20of%20state.%20He%20has%20maintained%20solid%20relations%20with%20essentially%20all%20factions%20of%20the%20Republican%20Party%2C%20and%20could%20likely%20be%20confirmed%20with%20ease%20in%20the%20Senate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20served%20as%20U.S.%20ambassador%20to%20Japan%20in%20the%20first%20Trump%20administration%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20president%20touted%20his%20warm%20relationship%20with%20then-Prime%20Minister%20Shinzo%20Abe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHagerty's%20policies%20are%20broadly%20in%20line%20with%20Trump's.%20Earlier%20in%20the%20year%2C%20he%20voted%20against%20a%20major%20military%20aid%20package%20for%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMARCO%20RUBIO%2C%20potential%20secretary%20of%20state%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERubio%2C%20a%20U.S.%20senator%20from%20Florida%20and%202016%20Republican%20presidential%20candidate%2C%20is%20also%20a%20top%20secretary%20of%20state%20contender%20whose%20policies%20hew%20closely%20to%20those%20of%20Trump.%20Like%20Hagerty%2C%20he%20was%20a%20contender%20to%20be%20Trump's%202024%20running%20mate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERubio%20has%20long%20been%20involved%20in%20foreign%20affairs%20in%20the%20Senate%2C%20particularly%20as%20it%20relates%20to%20Latin%20America%2C%20and%20he%20has%20solid%20relationships%20throughout%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMIKE%20WALTZ%2C%20potential%20defense%20secretary%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20former%20Army%20Green%20Beret%20who%20is%20currently%20a%20U.S.%20congressman%20from%20Florida%2C%20Waltz%20has%20established%20himself%20as%20one%20of%20the%20foremost%20China%20hawks%20in%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20various%20China-related%20bills%20he%20has%20co-sponsored%20are%20measures%20designed%20to%20lessen%20U.S.%20reliance%20on%20critical%20minerals%20mined%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWaltz%20is%20on%20speaking%20terms%20with%20Trump%20and%20is%20widely%20considered%20to%20be%20a%20serious%20contender%20for%20secretary%20of%20defense.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKEITH%20KELLOGG%2C%20potential%20candidate%20for%20national%20security%20adviser%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20retired%20lieutenant%20general%20who%20served%20as%20chief%20of%20staff%20to%20the%20National%20Security%20Council%20under%20Trump%2C%20Kellogg%20has%20Trump's%20ear%20and%20is%20a%20contender%20for%20national%20security%20adviser%2C%20among%20other%20national%20security%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20campaign%2C%20he%20presented%20Trump%20with%20a%20plan%20to%20end%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20which%20involved%20forcing%20both%20parties%20to%20the%20negotiating%20table%20and%20ruling%20out%20NATO%20membership%20for%20Ukraine%20for%20the%20foreseeable%20future%2C%20among%20other%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMARK%20GREEN%2C%20potential%20homeland%20security%20secretary%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20former%20Army%20flight%20surgeon%20and%20the%20current%20chair%20of%20the%20House%20Homeland%20Security%20Committee%2C%20Green%20is%20considered%20by%20some%20Trump%20allies%20in%20Washington%20as%20a%20contender%20for%20the%20top%20job%20at%20the%20Department%20of%20Homeland%20Security%20.%20His%20supporters%20describe%20him%20as%20a%20Trump%20loyalist%20and%20immigration%20hardliner%20who%20also%20has%20significant%20legislative%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGreen%20was%20nominated%20by%20Trump%20during%20his%20first%20term%20to%20serve%20as%20secretary%20of%20the%20Army%2C%20but%20he%20withdrew%20his%20name%20as%20past%20statements%2C%20which%20were%20widely%20seen%20as%20transphobic%20and%20Islamophobic%2C%20drew%20more%20scrutiny.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJOHN%20RATCLIFFE%2C%20potential%20attorney%20general%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20former%20congressman%20and%20prosecutor%20who%20served%20as%20director%20of%20national%20intelligence%20during%20Trump's%20last%20year%20in%20office%2C%20Ratcliffe%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20potential%20attorney%20general%2C%20though%20he%20could%20also%20take%20a%20separate%20national%20security%20or%20intelligence%20position%2C%20such%20as%20CIA%20director.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20president-elect's%20allies%20view%20Ratcliffe%20as%20a%20hardcore%20Trump%20loyalist%20who%20could%20likely%20win%20Senate%20confirmation.%20Still%2C%20during%20his%20time%20as%20director%20of%20national%20intelligence%2C%20Ratcliffe%20often%20contradicted%20the%20assessments%20of%20career%20civil%20servants%2C%20drawing%20criticism%20from%20Democrats%20who%20said%20he%20politicized%20the%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMIKE%20LEE%2C%20potential%20attorney%20general%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20U.S.%20senator%20from%20Utah%2C%20Lee%20is%20widely%20seen%20as%20another%20top%20candidate%20for%20attorney%20general.%20Though%20the%20former%20prosecutor%20declined%20to%20vote%20for%20Trump%20during%20the%202016%20election%2C%20he%20later%20became%20an%20unwavering%20ally%2C%20and%20he%20has%20become%20something%20of%20an%20intellectual%20he