0by%20G7%20member%20states%20-%20UK%2C%20Italy%2C%20and%20Japan.%20The%20approval%20was%20given%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Starmer%20and%20his%20cabinet%20gave%20the%20approval%20for%20the%20Global%20Combat%20Aircraft%20Programme%20or%20GCAP%2C%20and%20a%20formal%20announcement%20of%20the%20project%20is%20likely%20in%20the%20next%20few%20weeks%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22No%20follow%2C%20no%20index%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2Faab8c68b-eb7e-4305-989c-d107cb931f4b%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20GCAP%20programme%20aims%20to%20counter%20a%20rising%20threat%20from%20Russia%20and%20China.%20The%20project%20will%20merge%20two%20different%20military%20programs%20-%20UK%20and%20Italy's%20Tempest%20Project%2C%20for%20which%20the%20UK%20had%20already%20pledged%20the%20initial%202-billion-pounds%2C%20and%20Japan's%20F-X%20programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EItaly%2C%20Japan%2C%20and%20the%20UK%20had%20signed%20a%20treaty%20in%20December%20last%20year%2C%20however%2C%20there%20was%20uncertainty%20over%20UK's%20participation%20due%20to%20the%20Labour%20Party's%20Strategic%20Defence%20Review%20or%20SDR%20which%20could%20scrap%20UK's%20participation%20on%20grounds%20of%20high%20costs.%20However%2C%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Starmer's%20go-ahead%2C%20those%20fears%20have%20been%20laid%20to%20rest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Image%20Credit%3A%20baesystems.com%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Image%20Credit%3A%20baesystems.com%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F6scuj0h_gcap-6th-generation-stealth-fighter-jet_625x300_11_November_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Csmall%3EImage%20Credit%3A%20baesystems.com%3C%2Fsmall%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20cost%20of%20the%20multi-billion-dollar%20project%20is%20not%20known%20yet%2C%20but%20the%20target%20to%20develop%20and%20commission%20the%20stealth%20fighter%20jet%20has%20been%20set%20for%202035.%20The%20project%20is%20being%20jointly%20developed%20by%20British%20aircraft%20manufacturer%20BAE%20Systems%2C%20engine%20manufacturer%20Rolls-Royce%2C%20Italy's%20Leonardo%20Aerospace%2C%20and%20Japan's%20Mitsubishi%20Heavy%20Industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20trilateral%20agreement%2C%20the%20joint%20GCAP%20government%20headquarters%20will%20be%20based%20in%20the%20UK.%20%26quot%3BUK%20is%20a%20proud%20member%20of%20the%20Global%20Combat%20Air%20Programme%2C%20working%20together%20with%20our%20partners%20Japan%20and%20Italy%2C%20we%20are%20fully%20focused%20on%20delivering%20a%20next-generation%20combat%20aircraft%20for%202035%2C%26quot%3B%20UK's%20Defence%20Ministry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20deadlines%20are%20met%2C%20the%20GCAP%20supersonic%2C%206th%20generation%20stealth%20fighter%20aircraft%20will%20become%20only%20the%20second%20such%20fighter%20jet%20in%20the%20world%20after%20the%20United%20States'%20B-21%20Raider%20Bomber%20which%20is%20manufactured%20by%20Northrop%20Grumman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETHE%20'B-21%20RAIDER'%20BOMBER%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20B-21%20Raider%20bomber%20has%206th%20generation%20stealth%20technology%2C%20advanced%20networking%20capabilities%20and%20an%20open%20systems%20architecture.%20It%20is%20made%20with%20stealth%20materials%20which%20defeat%20the%20anti-access%2C%20area-denial%20systems%20it%20faces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20Credit%3A%20northropgrumman.com%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Photo%20Credit%3A%20northropgrumman.com%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fpb2qljso_b-21-raider-bomber-6th-gen-stealth-fighter_625x300_11_November_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Csmall%3E%3Cem%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20northropgrumman.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsmall%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20capable%20of%20delivering%