e%20government's%20building%20construction%20department%20had%20given%20a%20notice%20to%20Mr%20Paras%2C%20asking%20him%20to%20vacate%20the%20office.%20He%20was%20given%20time%20till%20November%2013%2C%20but%20the%20office%20was%20vacated%20before%20the%20deadline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Paras%2C%20a%20former%20Union%20Minister%2C%20had%20pleaded%20before%20all%20the%20top%20BJP%20leaders%20in%20Delhi%20to%20save%20this%20house%20and%20office.%20But%20before%20Chirag%20Paswan's%20stubbornness%2C%20no%20one%20prevailed%2C%20party%20sources%20said%20on%20strict%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChirag%20Paswan%20had%20been%20humiliated%20once%20after%20the%20split%20in%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20years%20ago%2C%20he%20was%20evicted%20from%20the%20bungalow%20in%20Delhi%20that%20had%20almost%20become%20his%20father's%20permanent%20home.%20Ramvilas%20Paswan%20was%20neighbour%20of%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20--%20his%2012%20Janpath%20Road%20residence%20was%20practically%20next%20door%20to%2010%20Janpath%2C%20one%20of%20the%20best-known%20addresses%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20March%202022%2C%20Chirag%20Paswan%20was%20evicted.%20Images%20from%20the%20spot%20showed%20the%20Paswan%20family's%20belongings%20heaped%20on%20the%20road%20along%20with%20photos%20of%20Ram%20Vilas%20Paswan.%20%26quot%3BThey%20threw%20my%20father's%20photo...%20We%20had%20such%20cherished%20photos.%20They%20walked%20on%20the%20photos%20with%20slippers%20on...they%20wore%20slippers%20all%20over%20the%20beds%2C%26quot%3B%20Chirag%20Paswan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20he%20had%20blamed%20Pashupati%20Paras%2C%20who%20shortly%20before%20had%20split%20the%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20and%20was%20rewarded%20with%20a%20cabinet%20berth.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnPaswan%20Junior%20had%20accused%20him%20of%20looking%20the%20other%20way%20during%20the%20alleged%20mayhem%20by%20security%20forces%20during%20the%20eviction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20the%20shoe%20was%20on%20the%20other%20foot.%20After%20Mr%20Paras'%20faction%20of%20LJP%20was%20summarily%20dropped%20by%20the%20BJP%20during%20the%20seat%20sharing%2C%20and%20his%20own%20faction's%20laudable%20performance%2C%20Chirag%20Paswan%20was%20not%20ready%20to%20relent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPashupati%20Paras%20had%20got%20the%20bungalow%20four%20decades%20ago%20during%20his%20tenure%20as%20an%20MLA.%20But%20later%2C%20after%20he%20lost%20an%20election%2C%20the%20house%20was%20allotted%20in%20the%20name%20of%20the%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20Ramvilas%20Paswan%20had%20a%20separate%20home%2C%20where%20he%20lived%20with%20his%20wife%20and%20son%2C%20he%20was%20mostly%20to%20be%20found%20at%20the%20party%20office.%20It%20was%20also%20the%20first%20stop%20when%20the%20former%20Union%20minister%20flew%20home%20from%20Delhi.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731342840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F3g0c9jno_pashupati-paras-eviction-_625x300_11_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funcle-pashupati-paras-evicted-from-home-chirag-paswan-has-the-last-laugh-6996247%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pashupati%20Paras%2C%20Chirag%20Paswan's%20rebel%20uncle%20who%20split%20his%20party%20and%20had%20him%20in%20a%20tight%20corner%20once%2C%20has%20been%20evicted%20from%20the%20building%20that%20had%20been%20his%20home%20for%20around%2040%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Sean%20Diddy%20advised%20this%20to%20young%20children%20on%20Rosie%20O'Donnell%20show.%20Old%20video%20viral%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731342090000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-115188405%2Cimgsize-875940.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwhen-sean-diddy-advised-this-to-young-children-on-rosie-odonnell-show-old-video-viral%2Farticleshow%2F115188397.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F115188397.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EIn%20the%201997%20episode%2C%20Rosie%20asked%20Diddy%20about%20his%20success.%20%26quot%3BWe%20feel%20blessed%2C%20we%20thank%20God%20for%20everything.%20We%20constantly%20pray%20and%20know%20that%20he's%20responsible%20for%20everything%20that%20has%20been%20blessed%20and%20granted%20to%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Diddy%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20what%20we%20try%20to%20tell%20young%20kids%2C%20that%20it's%20important%20to%20have%20God%20in%20your%20life.%26quot%3B%20The%20Youtube%20video%20is%20going%20viral%20as%20Diddy%20is%20accused%20of%20raping%20minors.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwhen-sean-diddy-advised-this-to-young-children-on-rosie-odonnell-show-old-video-viral%2Farticleshow%2F115188397.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwhen-sean-diddy-advised-this-to-young-children-on-rosie-odonnell-show-old-video-viral%2Famp_articleshow%2F115188397.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwhen-sean-diddy-advised-this-to-young-children-on-rosie-odonnell-show-old-video-viral%2Famp_articleshow%2F115188397.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Triveni%20Turbine%20Q2%20results%3A%20PAT%20rises%2042%25%20to%20Rs%2091%20cr%20on%20higher%20income%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731341378000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Ftriveni-turbine-q2-results-pat-rises-42-to-rs-91-cr-on-higher-income-124111101523_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20posted%20a%20Profit%20After%20Tax%20(PAT)%20of%20Rs%2064%20crore%20in%20the%20July-September%20quarter%20of%20preceding%202023-24%20financial%20year%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMy%20Karmabhoomi%26quot%3B%3A%20Milind%20Deora%20On%20Worli%20Battle%20vs%20Aaditya%20Thackeray%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EShinde%20Sena%20leader%20Milind%20Deora%20spoke%20to%20NDTV%20Monday%20-%20over%20dosa%20and%20some%20chai%2C%20a%20welcome%20break%20from%20a%20busy%20election%20schedule%20-%20about%20next%20week's%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%20poll%20contest%20against%20Aaditya%20Thackeray%20of%20the%20Thackeray%20Shiv%20Sena%20faction%2C%20and%20underlined%20his%20'local'%20credentials%20to%20voters.%20Mr%20Deora%20will%20contest%20the%20Worli%20seat%20in%20south%20Mumbai%20-%20a%20current%20stronghold%20of%20the%20Thackeray%20Sena%20faction%20and%20won%20convincingly%20by%20Aaditya%20Thackeray%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20me...%20I%20am%20a%20south%20Mumbaikar.%20I%20was%20born%20here%2C%20I%20live%20here%2C%20I%20work%20here.%20This%20is%20my%20janmbabhoomi%20and%20karmabhoomi.%20No%20doubt%20Aaditya%20Thackeray%20is%20an%20important%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%20and%20has%20been%20MLA%20for%20five%20years.%20So%2C%20in%20some%20ways%2C%20this%20is%20a%20political%20challenge.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20wanted%20to%20mount%20a%20serious%20challenge%20for%20this%20seat...%20to%20raise%20the%20stakes.%20We%20did%20think%20about%20giving%20the%20ticket%20a%20local%20leader%2C%20but%20the%20decision%20was%20finally%20taken%20that%20I%20should%20contest.%20It%20was%20felt%20that%20giving%20the%20seat%20to%20a%20local%20person%20can%20swing%20both%20ways.%20What%20could%20have%20happened%20is%20that%20the%20opposition%20could%20say%2C%20'it%20is%20an%20unknown%20person'%20and%20there%20could%20be%20conspiracies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fight%20for%20Worli%2C%20therefore%2C%20is%20set%20to%20be%20a%20high-profile%20battle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20earlier%20interview%20with%20NDTV%20Mr%20Deora%20had%20played%20down%20any%20talk%20of%20a%20'personal'%20contest%20with%20Aaditya%20Thackeray%2C%20saying%20he%20had%20known%20Aaditya%20Thackeray%20%26quot%3Bsince%20his%20childhood%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20he%20would%20not%20speak%20ill%20of%20the%20young%20politician.%20He%20did%2C%20however%2C%20criticise%20him%20and%20his%20party's%20failure%20to%20develop%20Worli%2C%20declaring%20residents%20were%20%26quot%3Btired%20of%20speed%20breaker%20politics%26quot%3B%20hampering%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMilind%20Deora%20is%20a%20former%20Congress%20leader%20who%20left%20that%20party%20in%20January%2C%20weeks%20before%20the%20general%20election%2C%20and%20joined%20the%20Sena%20faction%20led%20by%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%2C%20who%20led%20rebel%20lawmakers%20into%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP.%20His%20candidature%20for%20this%20seat%20was%20confirmed%20late%20last%20month%2C%20and%20immediately%20the%20headlines%20were%20about%20a%20Sena%20vs%20Sena%20fight%20for%20Worli.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20lots%20of%20good%20workers%20here...%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Deora%20told%20NDTV%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20selection%20process%20that%20led%20to%20him%20getting%20the%20Worli%20ticket%2C%20a%20choice%20he%20jokingly%20called%20%26quot%3Ba%20left-field%20decision%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20area%20is%20different...%20it%20is%20cosmopolitan%20and%20has%20a%20strong%20local%20identity.%20Many%20here%20identify%20as%20'Worlikars'.%20Worli%20also%20has%20had%20local%20leader%20serving%20as%20MLAs.%20In%20that%20sense%2C%20Aaditya%20was%20the%20first%20'outsider'%20MLA%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20taking%20a%20jab%20at%20his%20rival%20even%20as%20he%20emphasised%20his%20local%20connect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Worli%20seat%20is%20in%20the%20Mumbai%20(South)%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%20that%20is%20widely%20seen%20as%20the%20backyard%20of%20the%20Deora%20family%3B%20Murli%20Deora%20won%20this%20seat%20four%20times%2C%20including%20a%20hat-trick%20of%20wins%20from%201984%20to%201991%2C%20and%20his%20son%2C%20Milind%20Deora%2C%20claimed%20two%20consecutive%20wins%20-%20in%202004%20and%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20since%20then%20the%20Sena%20has%20held%20Mumbai%20(South).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20March%20the%20Shinde%20Sena%20gave%20its%20new%20recruit%2C%20Milind%20Deora%2C%20the%20responsibility%20of%20leading%20its%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20charge%20in%20the%20Mumbai%20(South)%20constituency.%20And%20he%20did%20a%20credible%20job%3B%20Arvind%20Sawant's%20winning%20margin%20dropped%20from%201.28%20lakh%20votes%20in%202019%20to%20just%20about%20one%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20margin%20of%20Aaditya%20Thackeray's%20win%20in%20the%202019%20state%20election%20-%20he%20had%20a%2065%20per%20cent%20vote%20share%20advantage%20-%20underlines%20the%20magnitude%20of%20the%20task%20for%20the%20Shinde%20Sena%20and%20Milind%20Deora.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20will%20also%20face-off%20against%20Sandeep%20Deshpande%20of%20the%20Maharashtra%20Navnirman%20Sena%20of%20Raj%20Thackeray%2C%20who%20is%20Uddhav%20Thackeray's%20cousin.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731341160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fuvrqjgkg_milind-deora-worli-assembly-constituency-ndtv-interview_625x300_29_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharashtra-assembly-election-my-karnabhoomi-milind-deora-on-worli-battle-vs-aaditya-thackeray-6995156%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shinde%20Sena%20leader%20Milind%20Deora%20spoke%20to%20NDTV%20Monday%20-%20over%20dosa%20and%20some%20chai%2C%20a%20welcome%20break%20from%20a%20busy%20election%20schedule%20-%20about%20next%20week's%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%20poll%20contest%20against%20Aaditya%20Thackeray%20of%20the%20Thackeray%20Shiv%20Sena%20faction%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2210%20Suspected%20Kuki%20Insurgents%20Killed%20In%20Gunfight%20In%20Manipur%2C%20Curfew%20Imposed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAt%20least%2010%20suspected%20Kuki%20insurgents%20were%20shot%20dead%20in%20an%20encounter%20with%20the%20security%20forces%20in%20Manipur's%20Jiribam%20district%20today%2C%20sources%20said.%20A%20Central%20Reserve%20Police%20Force%20(CRPF)%20soldier%20was%20injured%20in%20the%20attack%20by%20the%20suspected%20Kuki%20militants%20in%20the%20district%20bordering%20Assam%2C%20sources%20said.%20The%20soldier%20was%20evacuated%20to%20Silchar%20Medical%20College%20in%20Assam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20encounter%20began%20after%20the%20suspected%20Kuki%20insurgents%20launched%20a%20massive%20attack%20from%20two%20sides%20on%20a%20police%20station%20in%20Jiribam%2C%20sources%20said.%20There%20is%20also%20a%20relief%20camp%20for%20internally%20displaced%20people%20next%20to%20the%20police%20station.%20The%20attackers%20may%20have%20looked%20to%20target%20the%20camp%20too%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attackers%20likely%20came%20in%20autorickshaws%2C%20a%20police%20officer%20told%20NDTV%20on%20phone%20from%20Jiribam.%20This%20police%20station%20in%20Jiribam's%20Borobekra%20had%20been%20targeted%20several%20times%20in%20recent%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20attacking%20the%20police%20station%2C%20the%20suspected%20Kuki%20insurgents%20spread%20out%20towards%20a%20small%20settlement%20in%20Jakurador%20Karong%2C%201%20km%20from%20the%20police%20station%2C%20and%20began%20setting%20houses%20on%20fire%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20adding%20they%20simultaneously%20engaged%20in%20a%20gunfight%20with%20the%20security%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECRPF%20has%20sent%20reinforcements%20to%20Jiribam%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C