ng%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20on%20a%20Hybrid%20Model%20system%20as%20of%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20reliable%20PCB%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20hybrid%20model%20was%20followed%20during%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20last%20year%2C%20when%20India's%20matches%20were%20held%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%20while%20other%20matches%20were%20played%20in%20Pakistan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20email%20is%20to%20be%20sent%20to%20the%20ICC%20with%20the%20advice%20of%20its%20legal%20department%20in%20which%20the%20Board%20wanted%20clarifications%20from%20the%20ICC%20on%20the%20Indian%20decision%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20of%20now%20the%20entire%20situation%20is%20being%20gauged%20by%20the%20PCB.%20No%20decision%20has%20been%20taken%20on%20the%20next%20step.%20Yes%20the%20PCB%20is%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20government%20for%20consultation%20and%20directives%20if%20required%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20source%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20source%20said%20the%20PCB%20was%20awaiting%20policy%20guidelines%20from%20the%20government%20regarding%20India%2C%20which%20will%20be%20cited%20to%20seek%20clarification%20from%20the%20ICC%20about%20India's%20refusal%20to%20participate.%C2%A0He%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20there%20could%20be%20legal%20implications%20for%20the%20ICC%20if%20the%20Pakistan%20government%20decides%20to%20take%20a%20tough%20call%20on%20cricket%20relations%20with%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731339000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F1rvvhgg_india-pakistan-afp_625x300_06_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fpakistan-may-withdraw-from-champions-trophy-2025-after-indias-refusal-to-travel-report-6995748%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20PCB%20was%20told%20by%20the%20ICC%20that%20BCCI%20won't%20send%20its%20team%20to%20Pakistan%20after%20the%20decision%20was%20communicated%20to%20the%20world%20governing%20body%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20Maternity%20Leave%20In%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20State%20Schools%2C%20Claim%20Guest%20Teachers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWomen%20guest%20teachers%20across%20government%20schools%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20are%20seeking%20provisions%20for%20paid%20maternity%20leaves%2C%20similar%20to%20those%20provided%20to%20their%20permanent%20counterparts%2C%20amid%20fears%20of%20facing%20termination%20or%20being%20forced%20to%20resign%2C%20even%20as%20the%20administration%20recently%20held%20a%20meeting%20to%20review%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPermanent%20teachers%20at%20state%20government-run%20schools%20are%20entitled%20to%20180%20days%20of%20paid%20maternity%20leaves.%20Guest%20teachers%2C%20however%2C%20are%20not%20provided%20such%20benefits%20and%20face%20the%20risk%20of%20salary%20deduction%20in%20case%20they%20go%20on%20maternity%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20got%20pregnant%2C%20they%20(school%20administration)%20encouraged%20me%20to%20keep%20working%2C%20saying%20they%20would%20look%20into%20it%20if%20a%20rule%20(not%20being%20entitled%20to%20paid%20maternity%20leaves)%20existed.%20After%20my%20delivery%2C%20I%20was%20forced%20to%20quit%20my%20job.%20I%20never%20wanted%20to%20quit%3B%20the%20school%20administration%20)%20had%20promised%20me%20that%20I%20would%20be%20informed%20of%20any%20changes.%20I%20received%20no%20updates%20and%20I%20wasn't%20informed%20before%20my%20name%20was%20removed%20(from%20the%20guest%20teachers'%20list).%20I%20belong%20to%20a%20middle%20class%20family%20and%20losing%20this%20job%20has%20been%20very%20challenging.%20It's%20been%20two%20years%2C%20and%20I%20still%20have%20no%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20Priya%20Nema%2C%20who%20worked%20as%20a%20guest%20teacher%20at%20a%20Government%20school%20in%20Kalapeepal%2C%20Shajapur%20district%2C%20said.%20She%20joined%20on%20July%2022%2C%202019%20and%20was%20removed%20on%20November%201%2C%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20Jagdish%20Parmar%20said%20his%20daughter-in-law%20(who%20is%20a%20guest%20teacher%20at%20a%20school)%20is%20pregnant%20and%20has%20been%20advised%20bed%20rest%2C%20but%20is%20unable%20to%20go%20on%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20had%20suffered%20a%20miscarriage%20once%20earlier.%20Now%2C%20doctors%20have%20advised%20her%20bed%20rest%20but%20she%20is%20unable%20to%20do%20so%20because%20of%20her%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20Parmar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20the%20government%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20had%20issued%20an%20order%2C%20allowing%20unpaid%20maternity%20leaves%20to%20women%20guest%20teachers%20in%20government%20Colleges.%20But%20the%20guest%20teachers%20in%20schools%2C%20however%2C%20claimed%20they%20are%20still%20not%20allowed%20to%20opt%20for%20maternity%20leaves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGuest%20Teachers%20Association%20state%20secretary%2C%20Ravikant%20Gupta%2C%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20granted%20any%20leaves.%20Even%20when%20we%20are%20unwell.%20In%20February%202014%2C%20it%20was%20proposed%20to%20offer%2013%20days%20of%20leave%20and%20six%20months%20of%20maternity%20leave%20for%20women%2C%20but%20no%20official%20order%20has%20been%20issued.%20We've%20approached%20ministers%20and%20state%20officials%20with%20our%20request%20but%20in%20vain.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20in%20the%20state%20education%20department%20acknowledged%20the%20problem%20faced%20by%20pregnant%20women%20guest%20teachers%20at%20government%20institutes%2C%20saying%20it%20has%20prompted%20several%20of%20them%20to%20either%20quit%20or%20face%20termination%20without%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20reviewed%20the%20rules%20extensively%20and%20there%20are%20no%20such%20provisions%20for%20guest%20teachers.%20We%20haven't%20received%20any%20formal%20complaints%20so%20far%20but%20we%20have%20sought%20the%20guidance%20of%20higher%20authorities%20and%20are%20awaiting%20further%20instructions%2C%26quot%3B%20Bhopal%20district%20education%20officer%20Narendra%20Ahirwar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESocial%20worker%20Meeta%20Wadhwa%20expressed%20concerns%20over%20the%20absence%20of%20such%20provisions%20for%20pregnant%20women%20employees.%20%26quot%3BThe%20government%20has%20good%20provisions%20for%20regular%20employees%20but%20the%20guest%20teachers%20are%20left%20out.%20It%20is%20troubling%20that%20women%20are%20either%20forced%20to%20resign%20or%20denied%20leaves.%20This%20affects%20both%20their%20mental%20and%20physical%20health.%20This%20issue%20should%20be%20reconsidered%2C%26quot%3B%20Wadhwa%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731338700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-07%2Ftu6udi0o_school-generic-classroom-generic-unsplash-650_625x300_13_July_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fguest-teachers-claim-no-maternity-leave-in-madhya-pradesh-state-schools-6995688%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Women%20guest%20teachers%20across%20government%20schools%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20are%20seeking%20provisions%20for%20paid%20maternity%20leaves%2C%20similar%20to%20those%20provided%20to%20their%20permanent%20counterparts%2C%20amid%20fears%20of%20facing%20termination%20or%20being%20forced%20to%20resign.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Voting%20for%20John%20Thune%20is%20indefensible'%3A%20MAGA%20cautious%20ahead%20of%20Senate%20leadership%20election%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731338311000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-115186534%2Cimgsize-1167246.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fvoting-for-john-thune-is-indefensible-maga-cautious-ahead-of-senate-leadership-election%2Farticleshow%2F115186459.cms%22%2