e%22%3A%22Mystery%20Behind%20Russia's%20%26quot%3BSpy%20Whale%26quot%3B%20Revealed%20In%20New%20Documentary%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20well-known%20white%20beluga%20whale%20suspected%20of%20being%20a%20Russian%20spy%20may%20have%20been%20guarding%20%26quot%3BKremlin%20property%26quot%3B%20when%20it%20was%20found%20dead%20off%20Norway's%20coast%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2C%20noindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fprogrammes%2Fm002504p%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Edocumentary%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20whale%2C%20nicknamed%20Hvaldimir-a%20combination%20of%20the%20Norwegian%20word%20for%20whale%2C%20hval%2C%20and%20the%20name%20of%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin-%20was%20found%20floating%20in%20Risavika%20Bay%20in%20southern%20Norway%20in%20September.%20Fishermen%20first%20spotted%20the%2014-foot%20whale%20near%20Ingoya%20in%20northern%20Norway%20in%20April%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20beluga%20dubbed%20the%20%26quot%3Bspy%20whale%2C%26quot%3B%20was%20wearing%20a%20harness%20with%20a%20small%20camera%20and%20a%20buckle%20marked%20with%20%26quot%3BEquipment%20St%20Petersburg%2C%26quot%3B%20fueling%20suspicions%20of%20its%20role%20as%20a%20spy%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2C%20noindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fenvironment%2F2024%2Fnov%2F10%2Fnew-film-unravels-mystery-of-the-russian-spy-whale%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EGuardian%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ereported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%2010-month%20investigation%2C%20the%20BBC%20documentary%20Secrets%20of%20the%20Spy%20Whale%20uncovered%20evidence%20suggesting%20Hvaldimir%20may%20have%20been%20trained%20as%20a%20covert%20%26quot%3Bguard%20whale.%26quot%3B%20Speaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Observer%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20film%20director%20Jennifer%20Shaw%20noted%2C%20%26quot%3BOur%20findings%20about%20Hvaldimir's%20potential%20role%20bring%20us%20closer%20to%20solving%20the%20mystery%2C%20but%20they%20also%2