ya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh.%20A%20party%20delegation%2C%20led%20by%20Union%20minister%20Arjun%20Ram%20Meghwal%2C%20has%20submitted%20a%2010-page%20memorandum%20to%20the%20Commission%2C%20mentioning%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20speeches%20and%20remarks%20and%20sought%20that%20he%20be%20%26quot%3Bcensured%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Brestrained%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20comes%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20the%20Congress%20complaint%20on%20the%20BJP's%20%26quot%3Bcommunal%20ads%26quot%3B%20--%20the%20party%20today%20said%20the%20poll%20body%20has%20taken%20note%20of%20it.%C2%A0The%20party%20has%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20posting%20a%20misleading%20advertisement%20on%20social%20media%20that%20contained%20%26quot%3Bfalse%20information%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha%20or%20JMM%2C%20Congress%2C%20and%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20or%20RJD.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20filed%20its%20complaint%20today%20and%20Mr%20Meghwal%2C%20who%20led%20the%20delegation%20to%20the%20Commission%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20told%20them%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20spoke%20lies%20in%20Maharashtra...%20he%20said%20BJP%20wants%20to%20crush%20the%20Constitution%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20also%20said%20Mr%20Gandhi%20had%20falsely%20accused%20other%20states%20of%20%26quot%3Bstealing%20and%20snatching%20alleged%20opportunities%20from%20the%20State%20of%20Maharashtra%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reference%20was%20to%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20%26quot%3Btotally%20unverified%20claims...%20that%20Apple's%20iPhones%20and%20Boeing's%20airplanes%20are%20being%20manufactured%20in%20other%20states%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20Maharashtra%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20has%20been%20consistently%20making%20false%2C%20unverified%2C%20and%20baseless%20allegations%20against%20the%20BJP...%20solely%20to%20achieve%20electoral%20gains%20in%20the%20election%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP%20complained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20complaint%20--%20filed%20on%20Sunday%20--%20referred%20to%20an%20advertisement%20posted%20on%20Facebook%20on%20November%209%2C%20which%20the%20party%20claimed%20was%20%C2%A0in%20blatant%20violation%20of%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20said%20advertisement...%20false%20allegations%20and%20statements%20are%20being%20ascribed%20to%20leaders%20of%20the%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha%20(JMM)%2C%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20(INC)%20and%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD).%20Additionally%2C%20the%20leaders%20are%20being%20portrayed%20in%20a%20negative%20and%20false%20light%2C%20with%20the%20sole%20intent%20of%20propagating%20false%20and%20baseless%20narratives%20against%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20read.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20said%20advertisement%20BJP%20had%20first%20tried%20to%20use%20actors%20who%20resemble%20the%20leaders%20of%20JMM%2C%20INC%20and%20RJD.%20Consequently%2C%20the%20advertisement%20has%20tried%20to%20raise%20several%20blatantly%20false%20allegations%20against%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20JMM%2C%20INC%20and%20RJD.%20One%20of%20the%20allegations%20is%20that%20these%20leaders%20are%20Anti-Adivasi'%20(against%20the%20tribals)%20who%20are%20banding%20together%20under%20the%20garb%20of%20being%20Pro-Adivasis%20to%20ultimately%20serve%20their%20own%20personal%20agendas%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731332220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F0r6hkdo8_rahul-gandhi_625x300_19_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-congress-in-tit-for-tat-complaint-to-election-commission-6994838%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20has%20written%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20seeking%20a%20First%20Information%20Report%20against%20Congress's%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20party%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20over%20what%20they%20have%20called%20'lies%26quot%3B%20against%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20RSS.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-congress-in-tit-for-tat-complaint-to-election-commission-6994838%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Video%3A%20Hainan%20Airlines%20Flight%20Catches%20Fire%20Mid-Air%2C%20Turns%20Back%20To%20Rome%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20Hainan%20Airlines%20flight%20that%20departed%20from%20Fiumicino%20Airport%20in%20Rome%2C%20Italy%2C%20was%20forced%20to%20turn%20back%20shortly%20after%20takeoff%20due%20to%20a%20fire%20on%20board.%20The%20flight%20headed%20to%20Shenzhen%2C%20China%2C%20encountered%20trouble%20when%20a%20bird%20strike%20caused%20an%20engine%20failure.%20Italian%20Coast%20Guard%20officials%20reported%20that%20the%20bird%20strike%20posed%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20aircraft's%20249%20passengers%20and%2016%20crew%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20bird%20strikes%20are%20relatively%20common%2C%20they%20can%20be%20dangerous%2C%20especially%20if%20they%20impact%20an%20engine.%20Fortunately%2C%20the%20Boeing%20787%20Dreamliner%20safely%20returned%20to%20Fiumicino%20after%20dumping%20fuel%20over%20the%20sea.%20Despite%20the%20emergency%20landing%2C%20there%20were%20no%20reported%20delays%20to%20air%20traffic%2C%20according%20to%20an%20Italian%20airport%20official.%20Italian%20sources%20indicate%20that%20the%20plane%20will%20undergo%20thorough%20checks%20to%20assess%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20damage%2C%20as%20flames%20were%20visible%20on%20the%20right%20engine%20while%20the%20aircraft%20was%20in%20the%20air.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Dreamliner%20787-9%2C%20bound%20for%20Shenzhen%2C%20took%20off%20at%209%3A55%20a.m.%20local%20time%20and%20managed%20a%20safe%20landing%20following%20the%20incident.%20Bird%20strikes%20with%20aircraft%20are%20not%20rare%3B%20last%20year%2C%20The%20Mirror%20reported%20a%20similar%20