lled%20on%20the%20poll%20panel%20to%20act%20against%20the%20Congress%20MP%20for%20%26quot%3Bgross%20violation%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%2C%20referring%20to%20a%20section%20of%20speech%20in%20Mumbai%20last%20week%3B%20in%20a%20written%20complaint%20to%20the%20EC%20Monday%20afternoon%2C%20the%20BJP%20said%20Mr%20Gandhi%20had%20%26quot%3Bfalsely%20accused%20other%20states%20of%20stealing%20and%20snatching%20alleged%20opportunities%20from%20the%20State%20of%20Maharashtra%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20told%20them%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20spoke%20lies%20in%20Maharashtra...%20he%20said%20BJP%20wants%20to%20crush%20the%20Constitution%2C%26quot%3B%20Union%20Law%20Minister%20Arjun%20Ram%20Meghwal%2C%20who%20led%20the%20saffron%20party%20delegation%20that%20met%20top%20election%20officials%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reference%20was%20to%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20%26quot%3Btotally%20unverified%20claims...%20that%20Apple's%20iPhones%20and%20Boeing's%20airplanes%20are%20being%20manufactured%20in%20other%20states%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20Maharashtra%26quot%3B.%20The%20BJP%20declared%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20had%20made%20such%20statements%20even%20after%20being%20served%20a%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20in%20fact%2C%20the%20State%20of%20Maharashtra%20has%20topped%20in%20FDI%20(foreign%20direct%20investment)%20across%20India%20by%20receiving%20a%20total%20of%20Rs%2070%2C795%20crore%20from%20April%20to%20June%202024-25%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP%20told%20the%20EC%2C%20%26quot%3BRahul%20Gandhi%2C%20with%20his%20statements%2C%20is%20inciting%20youth%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%20which%20is%20immensely%20dangerous.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20only%20expected%2C%20and%20in%20line%20with%20his%20typical%20pattern%20of%20campaigning%20and%20general%20conduct%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20speech%20was%20full%20of%20falsehood%20and%20lies%2C%20intending%20to%20create%20disaffection%2C%20enmity%2C%20and%20ill-will%20between%20states%20of%20the%20Union%20of%20India...%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20wished%20to%20create%20a%20divide%20between%20the%20people%20of%20Maharashtra%20and%20other%20states%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ruling%20party%20alleged%20in%20its%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20has%20been%20consistently%20making%20false%2C%20unverified%2C%20and%20baseless%20allegations%20against%20the%20BJP...%20solely%20to%20achieve%20electoral%20gains%20in%20the%20election%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP%20complained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20referred%20to%20the%20EC's%20March%201%20advisory%20-%20issued%20before%20the%20April-June%20general%20election%20-%20in%20which%20it%20all%20political%20leaders%20were%20urged%20to%20%26quot%3Bobserve%20utmost%20restraint%20and%20decency%20in%20election%20campaigns%2C%20and%20to%20raise%20the%20level%20of%20election%20campaigning%20to%20'issue'%20based%20debates%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitical%20parties%20and%20their%20leaders%20%26quot%3Bshall%20not%20make%20false%20statements%2C%20or%20utterances%20without%20factual%20basis%2C%20aimed%20at%20misleading%20the%20voters%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20BJP%20said%2C%20reminding%20the%20EC%20of%20its%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20advisories%20have%20%26quot%3Blittle%20or%20no%20effect%20on%20the%20Congress%20and%20its%20leadership%20and%20star%20campaigners%2C%20and%20the%20electoral%20violations%20continue%20unabated%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20BJP%20said%2C%20calling%20on%20the%20poll%20panel%20to%20direct%20a%20police%20case%20be%20filed%20against%20Mr%20Gandhi%20and%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731326400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fg2ibmuqo_rahul-gandhi-ani_625x300_09_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcensure-and-restrain-rahul-gandhis-lies-bjp-to-election-commission-6993898%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20has%20said%20the%20Elec