ision%20aligned%20with%20the%20United%20Nations%E2%80%99%20Sustainable%20Development%20Goals%20(SDGs).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20incubating%20new%20startups%2C%20thingQbator%20also%20offers%20a%20myriad%20of%20learning%20opportunities%20for%20students%20across%20the%20country.%20This%20learning%20platform%20offers%20over%2018%20courses%20in%20hardware%20and%20software%20that%20students%20can%20complete%20at%20their%20convenience%20to%20enhance%20their%20technical%20skills.%20This%20platform%20is%20available%20to%20all%20students%20who%20register.%20The%20courses%20cover%20a%20range%20of%20topics%20%E2%80%94%20from%20building%20apps%20using%20Flutter%20to%20creating%20websites%2C%20web%20development%20skills%2C%20and%20working%20with%20Raspberry%20Pi%203%20%E2%80%94%20providing%20a%20high%20level%20of%20technical%20understanding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%2030%2C000%20course%20completion%20certificates%20have%20been%20issued%2C%20and%20over%2016%2C000%20unique%20students%20have%20received%20course%20completion%20certificates%20as%20of%20March%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20providing%20a%20platform%20that%20transcends%20entrepreneurial%20incubation%2C%20thingQbator%20is%20empowering%20young%20Indians%20to%20become%20the%20driving%20force%20behind%20technology%20and%20innovation.%20This%20initiative%20serves%20as%20a%20powerful%20catalyst%2C%20propelling%20the%20vision%20of%20a%20technologically%20advanced%20and%20socially%20empowered%20India%20into%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20truly%20believe%20it%20is%20crucial%20to%20ignite%20the%20imaginations%20of%20young%20minds%2C%20and%20universities%20and%20other%20educational%20institutions%20are%20the%20ideal%20environments%20to%20encourage%20them%20to%20explore%20new%20ideas.%20And%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20we%20aim%20to%20do%20through%20our%20thingQbator%20programme%20%E2%80%93%20we%20collaborate%20with%20universities%20to%20identify%20and%20mentor%20young%20minds%2C%20helping%20them%20shape%20and%20realize%20their%20entrepreneurial%20aspirations.%20This%20initiative%20is%20not%20just%20about%20nurturing%20startups%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20empowering%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20innovators%20to%20create%20impactful%20solutions%20for%20the%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Harish%20Krishnan%2C%20Managing%20Director%20%26amp%3B%20Chief%20Policy%20Officer%2C%20Cisco%20India%20%26amp%3B%20SAARC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%20%26amp%3B%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%20nasscom%20foundation%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731321261000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D378406%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20thingQbator%20programme%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Cisco%20and%20nasscom%20foundation%20initiative%20%E2%80%94%20nurtures%20young%20innovators%20by%20providing%20mentorship%2C%20funding%2C%20and%20resources%20to%20solve%20societal%20issues%20using%20technology.%20Since%202018%2C%20it%20has%20incubated%20over%2058%20startups%2C%20addressing%20challenges%20in%20education%2C%20agriculture%2C%20mental%20health%2C%20and%20accessibility%2C%20empowering%20students%20to%20become%20job%20creators%20and%20future-ready%20entrepreneurs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNo%20Champions%20Trophy%20Without%20India%26quot%3B%3A%20PCB%20Told%20'Hard%20Reality'%20By%20Ex-India%20Star%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20topic%20of%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%20is%20gaining%20all%20the%20public%20attention%20with%20every%20passing%20day.%20The%20tournament%20is%20slated%20to%20be%20hosted%20by%20Pakistan%20but%20Team%20India%20has%20refused%20to%20travel%20to%20the%20neighbouring%20country%2C%20citing%20the%20political%20tensions%20between%20the%20two%20nations.%20Since%202008%20Asia%20Cup%2C%20India%20are%20yet%20to%20visit%20Pakistan%20while%20the%201992%20world%20champions%20came%20to%20India%20for%20the%202023%20ODI%20World%20Cup.%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20also%20informed%20that%20they%20have%20received%20an%20email%20from%20the%20ICC%20regarding%20India's%20refusal%20to%20travel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20India%20opener%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Aakash%20Chopra%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F597-aakash-chopra-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAakash%20Chopra%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20gave%20his%20opinion%20on%20the%20matter%20and%20stated%20that%20if%20Team%20India%20opts%20out%2C%20then%20there%20will%20be%20no%20Champions%20Trophy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%2C%20this%20is%20an%20ICC%20event.%20Broadcasters%20have%20committed%20money%20for%20the%20event.%20But%20there%20is%20always%20a%20rider%20that%20if%20ICC%20cannot%20ensure%20India's%20participation%2C%20then%20the%20broadcasters%20will%20not%20invest%20or%20there%20will%20be%20a%20financial%20re-evaluation.%20If%20India%20does%20not%20participate%2C%20the%20money%20falls%20drastically%2C%26quot%3B%20Aakash%20said%20on%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCG90OGpA9Ow%3Fsi%3DfUK-4igIUZ5XVibY%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouTube%20channel%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20last%20PCB%20board%20chief%20during%20the%202023%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20said%20'%3Cem%3Edushman%20mulk%20ja%20rahe%20hum%3C%2Fem%3E'%20(we%20are%20going%20into%20the%20enemy's%20territory).%20In%20the%20future%2C%20if%20Pakistan%20decides%20not%20to%20play%20against%20India%2C%20there%20will%20be%20repercussions.%20India%20will%20also%20face%20repercussions%20if%20they%20do%20not%20visit%20Pakistan%2C%20but%20the%20sanctions%20will%20be%20financial%2C%20and%20how%20can%20the%20ICC%20stop%20India's%20money%20going%20to%20India%3F%20Pakistan%20do%20not%20have%20that%20kind%20of%20leverage.%20This%20is%20the%20hard%20reality.%20I%20feel%20it%20is%20absolutely%20certain%20that%20there%20will%20be%20no%20Champions%20Trophy%20without%20India.%20Every%20team%2C%20including%20Pakistan%2C%20understands%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20PCB%20chairman%20Mohsin%20Naqvi%20on%20Sunday%20initiated%20talks%20with%20senior%20government%20officials%20to%20discuss%20future%20course%20of%20action%20after%20ICC%20conveyed%20to%20PCB%20about%20India's%20unwillingness%20to%20tour%20the%20country%20for%20next%20year's%20Champions%20Trophy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMohsin%20Naqvi%2C%20who%20is%20the%20federal%20interior%20minister%2C%20is%20in%20touch%20with%20government%20officials%20and%20the%20wait%20is%20now%20on%20what%20directives%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20Shahbaz%20Sharif%20gives%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20PCB%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20expressed%20his%20disappointment%20over%20India's%20stand%20despite%20Pakistan%20promising%20full-scale%20security%20for%20the%20visitors%20during%20the%20ICC%20showpiece.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt's%20unacceptable%20as%20there%20is%20no%20logical%20reason%20for%20India%20to%20again%20refuse%20to%20send%20its%20team%20to%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPreparations%20for%20the%20event%20are%20on%20schedule%20and%20we%20have%20already%20assured%20the%20ICC%20of%20all%20the%20best%20security%20arrangements%20for%20all%20teams%20including%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20PTI%20Inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731320460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fi9tnj388_rohit-babar_625x300_13_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fno-champions-trophy-without-india-pcb-told-hard-reality-amid-bcci-sanction-talks-6993223%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Champions%20Trophy%202025%20is%20slated%20to%20be%20hosted%20by%20Pakistan%20but%20Team%20India%20has%20refused%20to%20travel%20to%20the%20neighbouring%20country%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagem