tage%20two%20or%20three%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Prabhat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatients%20have%20two%20options%3A%20opting%20for%20kidney%20transplants%20or%20undergoing%20dialysis.%20The%20former%20is%20expensive%20and%20comes%20with%20the%20added%20problem%20of%20lack%20of%20donors.%20For%20most%20patients%2C%20dialysis%20becomes%20the%20only%20viable%20option%20to%20ensure%20a%20good%20quality%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMissing%20dialysis%20sessions%20can%20lead%20to%20serious%20health%20complications%20as%20waste%20and%20fluids%20build%20up%20in%20the%20body.%20High%20potassium%20levels%20can%20disrupt%20heart%20rhythm%20and%20become%20life-threatening.%20Fluid%20overload%20may%20cause%20fluid%20retention%20in%20the%20lungs%2C%20leading%20to%20breathlessness%2C%20swollen%20ankles%2C%20high%20blood%20pressure%2C%20and%20even%20heart%20failure.%20Patients%20may%20also%20experience%20intense%20itching%2C%20extreme%20fatigue%2C%20and%20reduced%20appetite%2C%20further%20weakening%20their%20overall%20health.%20Regular%20dialysis%20is%20essential%20to%20manage%20these%20risks%20and%20maintain%20stability%20for%20those%20with%20kidney%20failure%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Saurabh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%20bootstrapped%2C%20the%20founders%20recently%20managed%20to%20raise%20a%20Series%20A%20round%20of%20investment.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20currently%20have%20centres%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20plan%20to%20deepen%20their%20presence%20in%20these%20states.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20journey%20has%20been%20very%20satisfying%20and%20full%20of%20learning.%20We%20want%20to%20provide%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F250227%2Fshashank-moddhia-mumbai-startup-renal-project-affordable-kidney-dialysis-in-india-healthcare-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekidney%20disease